en: The Neighborhood Compass is a primary community resource that allows you to track changes in your community with data; regularly-updated information that often deepens your gut-level understanding that the character of Durham’s neighborhoods is changing.
es: El Neighborhood Compass es un recurso fundamental que le permite seguir los cambios en su comunidad con información que es actualizada regularmente y que, a menudo, profundiza esa sensación visceral que usted tiene de que el carácter de los vecindarios de Durham está cambiando.

en: Explore your Durham neighborhood with this regularly-updated website. Find current data, create reports and maps, and track changes in your community. The best resource for accurate data about neighborhoods in Durham, North Carolina.
es: Explore su vecindario en Durham en este sitio web, que es actualizado regularmente. Encuentre información actualizada, genere reportes y mapas, y siga los cambios que ocurren en su comunidad. El mejor recurso para obtener información precisa sobre los vecindarios de Durham, Carolina del Norte.

en: Area containing containing between 1,200 and 8,000 people. Census tract boundaries usually follow features like major roads, rivers, or municipal boundaries. Most tracts contain one or two neighborhoods.
es: Area containing containing between 1,200 and 8,000 people. Census tract boundaries usually follow features like major roads, rivers, or municipal boundaries. Most tracts contain one or two neighborhoods.

en: A census blockgroup is made up of several city blocks and usually contains between 600 and 3,000 people. Sometimes a blockgroup is the size of a neighborhood, but most neighborhoods are larger than a single blockgroup.
es: A census blockgroup is made up of several city blocks and usually contains between 600 and 3,000 people. Sometimes a blockgroup is the size of a neighborhood, but most neighborhoods are larger than a single blockgroup.

en: The {compassLink} is a primary community resource for information that is regularly-updated, serving meaningful data to the community openly.
es: El {compassLink} es un recurso de información primario de la comunidad que es actualizado regularmente, que proporciona abiertamente valiosa información a la comunidad.

en: Each year the Compass grows and learns along with its users, adding data sets with strong community resonance and longitudinal importance.
es: Cada año el Compass crece y aprende junto con sus usuarios, sumando conjuntos de datos que tengan sentido para la comunidad y cuya importancia sea transversal.
